answer: Cosentyx's net sales in the immunology segment for full year 2024 were USD 50.8 billion (reported USD 46.3 billion, constant currency USD 48.7 billion), representing a 23% reported and 23% constant currency increase from full year 2023 (USD 36.2 billion, USD 31.7 billion, representing a 54% reported and 54% constant currency increase).
